title: The Ceraadi Interview
description:
Ceraadi is a sister duo signed to Roc Nation. Originally from Cedar Rapids, the sisters made their way to Long Beach then South Central. They have been growing their social media following including their YouTube posting videos on fashion, beauty, music, and relationship advice videos. Their YouTube has amassed over 1.2 million subscribers. The sisters Saiyr and Emaza came through the No Jumper studios for their first interview with Adam22 to talk about how they got their start, YouTube, and much more!
